             was indicted for <rs id="t17990220-3-off13" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17990220-3-off13" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17990220-3-off13" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17990220-3-cd14" type="crimeDate">1st of February</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17990220-3-off13 t17990220-3-cd14"></join>, eighteen pounds of mutton, value 6s.
            </rs> the property of 
               <persName id="t17990220-3-victim72" type="victimName">
                  Thomas 
                  Campion
               <interp inst="t17990220-3-victim72" type="surname" value="Campion"></interp>
